cmnh1skag0093k908v5gi6rus	cmnh1sk3c003tk908gigp09oy	personnel	Project Manager and Technical Lead: Tiago Rezende	month	14	6000	17640	This position serves as the primary technical and strategic lead for the initiative. Beyond project oversight and donor reporting, this role is directly responsible for the design and delivery of core training modules, including International Sustainable Business Models, Export Basics, and Joint Marketing Strategies. He will lead the Training of Operators and Quality Control Procedures at the shared maquila and provide specialized technical assistance in rural business development. His functions include the creation of educational content, the development of standardized operating procedures (SOPs), and ensuring that all project activities align with international trade requirements and the specific needs of the Los Santos agro-food sector.. $6,000/month x 14 months x 21% effort = $17,640. Fully funded by the project.	federal	\N	\N	0	t	2026-04-02 05:42:21.113	2026-04-02 05:42:21.113
cmnh1skag0094k908veezj8u7	cmnh1sk3c003tk908gigp09oy	personnel	Operations and Business Development Technician: Pablo Gonzalez	month	14	3000	8820	This role focuses on the direct execution of field-based technical support and business coaching. He is responsible for conducting the individualized coaching sessions for financial management, basic costing, and digital tool adoption. He will coordinate the baseline diagnostic process for all 30 MSMEs and lead the participatory development of Business Improvement and Export-Readiness Plans. Furthermore, he will provide ongoing mentorship in commercialization, digital marketing, and business formalization. His technical contribution includes the development of practical toolkits and educational materials for beneficiaries, ensuring that the operational transition from primary production to value-added processing is supported by robust business management practices. $3,000/month x 14 months x 21% effort = $12,600. Fully funded by project resources.	federal	\N	\N	1	t	2026-04-02 05:42:21.113	2026-04-02 05:42:21.113
